creator: MovingClocksCloud
descriptionHtml:
Introducing our privacy-focused Android browser app that offers lightning-fast web browsing, lightweight design, and seamless user experience. Our browser stands out from the competition with its advanced privacy model that prioritizes user privacy without compromising on the browsing speed.

Private Mode
Our browser's default incognito mode ensures that your online activity remains private and secure. It means that your browsing history, cookies, and other sensitive data won't get stored on your device, keeping your online identity anonymous.

Junk Scan
Cloak Browser will remind you to scan useless files to save memory space and prevent privacy leaks. We will prompt you to scan regularly in a prominent position on the homepage. These files are useless cache, logs, etc. generated when you use your phone, which may contain your personal privacy. Regular scanning helps prevent privacy leaks and use your phone more securely.

Knowledge Test
We have an exclusive fun quiz module that includes carefully selected interesting questions. By answering these questions, you can gain more knowledge, and if you encounter a difficult question, you can directly learn related terms from within the browser to enrich your knowledge. You can even invite your friends to participate and see who can answer more questions correctly. Come and join us!

Global News
We have carefully selected and delivered global news events to you, so you won't miss any hot topics and can easily stay informed of world events.

Overall, our privacy-focused Android browser app is the perfect solution for those looking for a lightweight and efficient browsing experience without sacrificing their privacy. Download it today and enjoy fast, secure, and private browsing!
descriptionShort: Stay anonymous online with our secure and private browser app.
